# UI: Dark mode, always

This project uses **dark mode only**. There is no light theme or toggle.

- Keep all UI (CSS, new components, forms, tables) using the dark palette.
- Use the existing CSS variables in `frontend/src/index.css`: `--bg`, `--bg-elevated`, `--bg-input`, `--text`, `--text-muted`, `--border`, `--accent`, `--error`.
- Do not introduce a light theme or theme switcher unless the user explicitly asks for it.
